a story of yonosuke ( 横道世之介 yokomichi yonosuke ) is a 2013 japanese film directed by shūichi okita .   the theme song is called " ima wo ikite " ( 今を生きて living in the now ) and is performed by asian kung-fu generation .   the film was shown at the 13th japanese film festival nippon connection on june 2013 .   it premiered in america on july 13 , 2013 at the new york asian film festival and has also made an appearance at the san diego asian film festival and the japanese film festival in australia .